# Getting started

https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/Add-ons/WebExtensions

# Installing/Testing the extension locally
1. Open "about:debugging" in Firefox
2. Click "Load Temporary Add-on" and select any file in your extension's directory


# Building a ZIP to upload to AMO
1. Open the src directory of the repository.
2. Select all of the files.
3. Right click and choose Send to â†’ Compressed (zipped) Folder.
